[Student "S"]
{SOUTH has both Majors and planned on bidding 1\H first, (up-the-line). 
But EAST's overcall gave SOUTH the opportunity to bid both Majors at the same time! Since the 
Negative Double promises both Majors it was like SOUTH could bid 1\H\S.

NORTH has \Ss so she bids 1\S, showing a minimum opener.

SOUTH has 13 points and the \S fit so he bids game.}

